</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">重庆市环保局<span> <br><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span>二○一<span>二</span>年七月二十四日</span></p>\n <p></p> \n <!--endprint--> \n <!--<$[CONTENT]>end--> \n</div>', '重庆市环保局2012年上半年面向基层公开遴选公务员拟遴选人员公示', '2012-07-26 00:00:00', 'http://www.cepb.gov.cn/doc/2012/07/26/30082.shtml');
