ght: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p style=\"layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"color: #2c2c2c\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体\">大渡口区李子林片区道路</span></span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 395px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p style=\"layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"color: #2c2c2c\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体\">道路严重破损，长期积泥积尘扬尘突出；重钢老厂区外出货运车辆带泥污染道路。</span></span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 150px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"color: #2c2c2c\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体\">大渡口区政府</span></span></span></p> </td> \n   </tr> \n   <tr> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 52px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman\">3</span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 340px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p style=\"layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"color: #2c2c2c\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体\">大渡口区蓝馨园安置房小区后荒地农作物焚烧</span></span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 395px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p style=\"layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"color: #2c2c2c\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体\">长期违法焚烧秸秆、树叶等污染大气环境。</span></span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 150px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"color: #2c2c2c\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体\">大渡口区政府</span></span></span></p> </td> \n   </tr> \n   <tr> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 52px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman\">4</span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 340px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p style=\"layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"color: #2c2c2c\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体\">江北区万兴路遂道工程</span></span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 395px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p style=\"layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"color: #2c2c2c\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体\">外出建筑运渣车冒装