: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_gb2312\">渝蓉高速大足段，铜永高速路沿线两侧违法焚烧</span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 346px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_gb2312\">高速路沿线两侧所属荣昌、永川、大足、铜梁等所在区县的农田和城区内违法焚烧秸秆、垃圾等污染大气环境。</span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 199px; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_gb2312\">永川区、铜梁区、荣昌区、大足区政府</span></span></p> </td> \n   </tr> \n  </tbody> \n </table> \n <p style=\"line-height: 20pt\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p></p> \n <!--endprint--> \n <!--<$[CONTENT]>end--> \n</div>', '第三批主城区及周边区县大气污染源被通报', '2016-09-05 00:00:00', 'http://www.cepb.gov.cn/doc/2016/09/05/144542.shtml');
INSERT INTO `site_info` VALUES ('199', '<h1>\n <!--<$[TITLE]>start-->3月份主城25个重点扬尘污染源因控尘不力被通报\n <!--<$[TITLE]>end--></h1><div id=\"Zoom\"> \n <!--<$[CONTENT]>start--> \n <p></p>\n <div> \n  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">&nbsp;</p> \n  <p style=\"text-indent:33.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3月9日，重庆市政府主城蓝天行动督查组通报了3月份主城区扬尘污染源巡查情况。经督查组近期在主城巡查发现，渝中区顺城街危旧房改造工程工地等25个项目尘污染问题较为突出，予以公开通报（见附表）。</span></span></p> \n  <p style=\"text-indent:33.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">市政府主城蓝天行动督查组介绍，扬尘污染严重影响空气中可吸入颗粒物（PM<sub>10</sub>）、细颗粒物（PM<sub>2.5</sub>）的浓度，进而严重影响主城区空气质量。督查组强调，各区政府和市政府有关部门务必加强所管辖范围及行业的工地、道路、码头、堆场、工业企业和建筑渣场扬尘的监督检查，及时发现扬尘污染隐患并督促整改。</span></span></p> \n  <p style=\"text-indent:33.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">对于本次被通报的污染源，市政府主城蓝天行动督查组要求，由主管部门依法查处并责令有关单位立即整改，将处理和整改情况于3月18日前书面回复督查组。</span></span></p> \n </div> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"line-height:30.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">附件</span></span></p> \n <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:30.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2016年3月主城区重点扬尘污染源明细表</span></span></p> \n <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:30.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;\">&nbsp;</p> \n <table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: none; width: 907px;\" width=\"977\"> \n  <tbody> \n   <tr> \n    <td style=\"width:59px;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt !msorm;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt !msorm;\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体_gbk;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\">序号</span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"width:216px;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt !msorm;border-left:none !msorm;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt !msorm;\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体_gbk;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\">未达标的污染源名单</span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"width:136px;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt !msorm;border-left:none !msorm;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt !msorm;\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体_gbk;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\">业主单位</span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"width:151px;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt !msorm;border-left:none !msorm;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt !msorm;\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体_gbk;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\">施工单位</span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"width:113px;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt !msorm;border-left:none !msorm;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt !msorm;\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体_gbk;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\">监管责任</span></span></p> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体_gbk;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\">单位</span></span></p> </td> \n    <td style=\"width:302px;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt !msorm;border-left:none !msorm;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt !msorm;\"> <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20.0pt;layout-grid-mode: